:929800,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T00:34:34.000Z","msg":"慢慢周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53041183e746138aec1315eba3975b047e5ff8d","tid":929800,"uid":62646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T00:47:29.000Z","msg":"華為官方回應<br />\n<br />\n近期，我們公司CFO孟晚舟女士在加拿大轉機時，被加拿大當局代表美國政府暫時扣留，美國正在尋求對孟晚舟女士的引渡，面臨紐約東區未指明的指控。<br />\n<br />\n關於具體指控提供給華為的信息非常少，華為並不知曉孟女士有任何不當行為。公司相信，加拿大和美國的法律體係會最終會給出公正的結論。<br />\n<br />\n華為遵守業務所在國的所有適用法律法規，包括聯合國、美國和歐盟適用的出口管製和製裁法律法規。<br />\n<br />\n華為"},{"pid":"c9a457823fddaf91eb263701ddb723aede981d19","tid":929800,"uid":73262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T00:58:47.000Z","msg":"叫吳京交完稅 快d去救人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f016c0bb9c1c564c3eb0b690c3af746daf90541","tid":929800,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a40382cc7fb70bd3cd598a526b472bce88341bd3","tid":929800,"uid":147454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T00:07:26.000Z","msg":"好好奇佢個女究竟會用華為定iphone"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:09:31.000Z","msg":"對大眾用華為 自己私人用iPhone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2bc34444b5a59a3dc47d1692453eb998cef1cc","tid":929800,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9a457823fddaf91eb263701ddb723aede981d19","tid":929800,"uid":73262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T00:58:47.000Z","msg":"叫吳京交完稅 快d去救人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce6e50db56301a2471639c8d31bb89c1ea72780","tid":929800,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"有BNO先係香港人"},{"pid":"a5c58c57c6a01b346ff66f31fa750c8e835bab60","tid":929800,"uid":47674,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:24:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/Assistance_Outside_Hong_Kong.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservices%2FAssistance_Outside_Hong_Kong.html&d=FUNJkixV47%2Bc3WPZyQz53kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ddb5c70e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/Assistance_Outside_Hong_Kong.html</a><br />\n<br />\n如 香 港 居 民 在 香 港 境 外 遇 事 ， 可 致 電 入 境 事 務 處 協 助 在 外 香 港 居 民 小 組 24 小 時 求 助 熱 線 尋 求 協 助 ， 熱 線 號 碼 為 ：<br />\n<br />\n(852) 1868<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/aa2233a/1195145173_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Faa2233a%2F1195145173_n.jpg&h=32bb3507&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db16695966f6256285bc02c9e0fb901c2988d42f","tid":929800,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:25:49.000Z","msg":"捉哂班國企高層去坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}